{"tid":1685833,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人皆尋夢","createTime":"2019-10-31T19:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T17:44:42.000Z","uid":431,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3475c47b911e65ae5e343c79393008ccada4a1bd","tid":1685833,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:17:59.000Z","msg":"天才白癡夢<br />\n<br />\n「天才與白癡」主題曲<br />\n作詞：許冠傑/薛志雄<br />\n作曲：許冠傑<br />\n<br />\n人皆尋夢，夢裡不分西東，<br />\n片刻春風得意，未知景物矇矓。<br />\n<br />\n人生如夢，夢裡輾轉吉凶，<br />\n尋樂不堪苦困，未識苦與樂同。<br />\n<br />\n天造之才，皆有其用，<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=0875aeee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n振翅高飛，無須在夢中。<br />\n<br />\n南柯長夢，夢去不知所蹤，<br />\n醉翁他朝醒覺，是否跨鳳乘龍。<br />\n<br />\n何必尋夢，夢裡甘苦皆空，<br />\n勸君珍惜此際，自當欣慰無窮。<br />\n<br />\n何必尋夢。"},{"pid":"6bf95f1842b52e9038fb7df4537c201ab64c91c7","tid":1685833,"uid":431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:18:20.000Z","msg":"我愛samhui 我愛samhui！"},{"pid":"a64cf78a431ba7da86b8f0f74a8cc53bd644d7f4","tid":1685833,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:18:45.000Z","msg":"都係同自己講"},{"pid":"30ae54350e6c7f5e53758b50cda0264db96c0c43","tid":1685833,"uid":218575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:26:02.000Z","msg":"@連仔<br />\n發現咗魔鏡歌詞網打手 <br />\n含有間接宣傳內容<br />\n請bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d303eeda892a14e362f1ba70269d5e8176b38054","tid":1685833,"uid":335391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T19:29:52.000Z","msg":"難分真與假　人面多險詐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81031633de43ccc78eedbe1603ef8e6bc9f4b02d","tid":1685833,"uid":129660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:10:26.000Z","msg":"好有智慧"},{"pid":"2e66710d2c5db990fd3c4e3413